Bot::CPAN
=========

INSTALLATION

To install this distribution type the following:

    cpansign -v (optional; requires Module::Signature to be installed)
    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

DEPENDENCIES

    Attribute::Handlers 0.78
    Class::Phrasebook 0.88
    Config::Auto 0.03 (optional; support for the 'cpanbot' wrapper script)
    CPANPLUS 0.042
    Encode 1.97 (optional; for utf8 decoding of cpanratings data)
    Getopt::Long 2.23 (optional; support for the 'cpanbot' wrapper script)
    HTTP::Request 1.30
    LWP::UserAgent 2.003
    Mail::Internet 1.58
    Math::Round 0.05
    Module::CPANTS 0.20030725 (optional; better guessing at dist descriptions)
    Module::Signature (optional; for distribution authenticity verification)
    Net::NNTP 2.22
    POE 0.26
    POE::Component::IRC 2.9
    Statistics::Descriptive 2.6
    URI 1.24
    XML::Parser 2.33
    XML::RSS::Parser 0.21
